      <title>野村证券将把年轻经纪公司员工的薪酬提高 16%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/nomura-will-lift-pay-by-16-for-younger-brokerage-staffers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村控股公司(Nomura Holdings Inc.)将在下一财年奖励其日本旗舰经纪子公司的年轻员工，平均加薪16%，远高于当地通胀率，这表明留住新员工的竞争加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/nomura-will-lift-pay-by-16-for-younger-brokerage-staffers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 05:05:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
