    <item>
      <title>因美联储观点和日本地震，日经 225 指数在第一个交易日下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/nikkei-225-falls-on-first-trading-day-on-fed-view-japan-quake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本日经 225 指数创下两周来最大跌幅，原因是市场猜测美联储将在较长时间内维持高利率，从而损害科技股，而且元旦当天西北地区发生的强烈地震拖累了一些公司。东证指数上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/nikkei-225-falls-on-first-trading-day-on-fed-view-japan-quake</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 02:31:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度债券自 2020 年以来首次实现年度收益后，前景看好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/stars-align-for-india-bonds-after-first-yearly-gain-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度主权债券创下三年来最佳年度表现，预计将进一步上涨，因为人们预期印度主权债券即将被纳入全球债券指数将吸引大量外资流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/stars-align-for-india-bonds-after-first-yearly-gain-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 02:13:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚停电和中东袭击导致油价连续第二天上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价走高——在周三上涨超过 3% 后——利比亚的供应中断和中东的袭击加剧了主要原油生产地区的紧张局势。]]></description>
